tool_description: This is fast and easy QR Code generator in different color. You will get the output result as PNG format.
title: RGBK QRcode

api_list.name: QR Code Green
api_list.description: This end point will generate Green QR Codes
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://rgbk-qrcode.p.rapidapi.com/qr-green/{data}"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "rgbk-qrcode.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
